query:
SELECT id, employeeId, courseId, confirmedCustomers, courseFee, calculatedRevenue, status, reviewedBy, reviewedAt 
FROM daily_stats 
WHERE status = 'approved' 
ORDER BY reviewedAt DESC 
LIMIT 5;
